query: select top (1) PerC.UniqueId, PerC.MiddleName Ent from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.MiddleName not like '%[a-zA-Z0-9?!_+=*\/%()}{<>^]%' and len(PerC.MiddleName) > 10 order by PerC.Birthdate desc

select top (1) PerC.UniqueId, substring(PerC.MiddleName, 3, len(PerC.MiddleName)-2) Ent from PersonCards PerC where PerC.IsDeleted != 1 and PerC.MiddleName not like '%[a-zA-Z0-9?!_+=*\/%()}{<>^]%' and len(PerC.MiddleName) > 11 order by PerC.Birthdate desc
